{"tid":1879127,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[港鐵有毒!] 黃大仙11名確診退伍軍人病, 港鐵細菌濃度超標","createTime":"2020-02-14T04:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T04:40:24.000Z","uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4cf2da1160aea4222426f0bd71d7df06ba61f4","tid":1879127,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"港鐵彩虹站冷卻塔退伍軍人桿菌濃度超標<br />\n3分鐘前<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】11名黃大仙居民確診退伍軍人病，衞生防護中心其後發現，港鐵彩虹站淡水冷卻塔退伍軍人桿菌濃度超標。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心調查11宗退伍軍人症個案，當中六人住彩虹邨、四人住坪石邨、一人住啟晴邨，年齡65至84歲，全部有長期病患。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心與機電工程署到病人居所及附近採樣本，經化驗後發現，在港鐵彩虹站四個淡水冷卻塔的水樣本中，有三個樣本的嗜肺性退伍軍人桿菌濃度超標。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，涉事水塔是散熱系統一部分，現已關閉及安排清洗消毒。"},{"pid":"1931c654d426d298d0c9fb436de908f96af1ce7d","tid":1879127,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T04:24:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=380560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380560&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR7KDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=2b91a5c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380560&h=f7e929ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=380560</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6009f8c17b77516e92341d206d6aea0fa13a6899","tid":1879127,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T04:40:24.000Z","msg":"又清算藍屍廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}